# EtherCAT Bring-up & Runtime Console

Open this notebook with a Mix project runtime rooted at this repository.

Use this notebook as the default manual test bench:

1. Run the setup smart cell and persist the generated `EtherCAT.start/1` code.
2. Wait for `EtherCAT.await_running/1`.
3. If the session stops at `:preop_ready`, call `EtherCAT.activate/0`.
4. Keep the runtime widgets open while you run hardware checks.

